95 Creating Blade Components

> php artisan make:component Button

   INFO  Component [C:\Users\Marco Julian\webapp4\app\View\Components\Button.php] created successfully.  

> php artisan make:component Forms/Button

   INFO  Component [C:\Users\Marco Julian\webapp4\app\View\Components\Forms\Button.php] created successfully.     


> php artisan make:component Forms/Link --inline

   INFO  Component [C:\Users\Marco Julian\webapp4\app\View\Components\Forms\Link.php] created successfully.  



96 Rendering Blade Components

> php artisan make:component inputField

   INFO  Component [C:\Users\Marco Julian\webapp4\app\View\Components\inputField.php] created successfully.  
   

